you need to care about.

00:14:49.860 --> 00:14:52.150
And after that, you can
start enjoying the app.

00:14:52.150 --> 00:14:56.630
You can browse and start
getting familiar with it,

00:14:56.630 --> 00:14:58.560
and you already have
done part of what

00:14:58.560 --> 00:15:01.970
you need to do to actually
be able to use it.

00:15:01.970 --> 00:15:03.970
But also, they remind
you of the other things

